00:28:41,090 --> 00:28:42,675
Dia membuatku takut.

440
00:28:42,758 --> 00:28:47,108
Astaga, Eric, jika dia sebahaya itu,
mungkin lebih baik kau memberitahuku namanya

441
00:28:47,346 --> 00:28:49,825
